  "title": "FleetOps and GroundOps and StarOps, Oh My",
  "summary": "Aboard the Star Destroyer Reprisal, the New Republic's Second Fleet gathers in dress uniform for a combined awards-and-promotion ceremony followed by a party. Admiral Ackbar presides, with the branch heads Crix Madine and Wedge Antilles handing out honors: Marines Wrista Ipex and Vengan Draelis are promoted and decorated for valor, gunner Rasi Cen and technician Javin Mitali are bumped to lieutenant junior grade, and Captain David Stone is elevated to Rear Admiral. The highlight is the promotion of the Chyleni pilot Kyrin Sh'vani to Captain and her receipt of the Silver Star and Star of Alderaan for escaping Imperial captivity, stealing a Star Destroyer, and helping bring about the death of Admiral Danik Kreldin; she delivers a heartfelt speech accepting the honors on behalf of all. Throughout, the rowdy Marines, irreverent Ghost Squadron pilots, and beaming friends trade jokes and cheers. Afterward, the assembly mingles over a buffet and Bith jazz, with Rasi securing Ackbar's autograph for his father and the friends learning that Mitali plans to retire soon before they all drift off.",
